  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPa28">
<l>kaṟavaikaḷ piṉ ceṉṟu kāṉam cērntuṇpōm</l>
<l>aṟivoṉṟum illāta vāyk kulattuntaṉṉaip</l>
<l>piṟavi peṟuntaṉaip puṇṇiyam yām uṭaiyōm</l>
<l>kuṟai yoṉṟum illāta kōvintā vuntaṉṉōṭu</l>
<l>uṟavēl namakkiṅkoḻikka voḻiyātu</l>
<l>aṟiyāta piḷḷaikaḷōm aṉpiṉāl untaṉṉai</l>
<l>ciṟu pēr aḻaittaṉavum cīṟi yaruḷātē</l>
<l>iṟaivā nī tārāy paṟaiyēlōr empāvāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Going behind the milch cows and reaching the woods,</l>
<l>we shall eat together.</l>
<l>We have merit enough to have You [take] birth</l>
<l>in the cowherd caste devoid of the least knowledge.</l>
<l>O Govinda without a single flaw!</l>
<l>As for [our] relation with You,</l>
<l>it will not be destroyed here [even if] we destroy it.</l>
<l>Pray do not be angry with us ignorant girls’ calling You</l>
<l>by petty names out of love!</l>
<l>O God! You give [us] paṟai drums!</l>
<l>O our maidens, accept [and] consider [this] attentively!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
